<div class="contacts-left">
  <h1> Contact Us </h1>
<br/>
  <h3>Where to find us:</h3>
  <p>
  1 Yishun St 23 #03-25/31/32<br/>
  YS-One Singapore 768441<br/>
  Office: (65)-67553933<br/>
  Fax:    (65)- 67555319<br/>
  Directions: Bus 811 from Yishun Bus interchange
  </p>

  <iframe width="400" height="400" frameborder="1" scrolling="no" marginheight="0" marginwidth="0" src="http://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&amp;hl=en&amp;geocode=&amp;q=Yishun+St+23,+Singapore&amp;sll=37.0625,-95.677068&amp;sspn=41.818029,92.8125&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;s=ABQIAAAA8wxcNXL5MYluvSTN5quHhRR5SAI2ndD6iMe-P7c1-pJihDhXxQeoYpQOaVjfMXbcWvrQizE6BA&amp;ll=1.449097,103.84655&amp;spn=0.025741,0.025749&amp;z=14&amp;iwloc=addr&amp;output=embed"></iframe>
